// This is the script Mel uses in the first and second fights
//
// Powers (other than various summonings that we take over verbatim:
//
// Heal 1/5 rds
// Vocalise at will
// Free action at will
// Stoneskin 1/5 rds
// Timestop once
// Truesight 1/10 rds
// Haste 1/3 rds
// Death spell 1/2 rds
// 
// and a Big Spell (these block one another for a bit):
//
// Earthquake 
// Unholy Word
// Sunray 
// Pierce Shield [Pierce Magic in SR]
// Dispel Magic
// Greater Malison
// Feeblemind
// Symbol: Fear
// Symbol: Death


